ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"都唔明驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能我小市民睇唔到咩程度<br />\n強極得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8069503621a0aaf9190d7df2cfc577752616724","tid":2149990,"uid":120660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"大亨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ff2117371470d6141278dd1b501e23be8b1115","tid":2149990,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"領事館d人囉"},{"pid":"06114ab7215f6fe1683dfeb8825e29b890551bf8","tid":2149990,"uid":169112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ea65b238f2fd1fbe89c4eed104a5adb6f41702c","tid":2149990,"uid":10998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡係咪真係當佢自己人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"樞機是教宗治理天主教會上主要的助手和顧問之職務，由教宗親自任命，是天主教會各級神職人員中僅次於教宗的職位，故有「教會親王」之稱。該職通常由具主教銜的神職人員出任，他們通常也是重要教區的正權主教或是聖座重要部門的首長。樞機的拉丁文原名為「cardo」（英文對應詞為「cardinal」），有鉸鏈、樞紐、重要的意思。另一字源為「incardinare」。樞機們組成樞機團[1]，當教宗職務出缺時，只有樞機團有權選舉下一任教宗，傳統上教宗也由樞機中選出。樞機禮服通常為紅色，故教外人士俗稱為紅衣主教。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%A8%9E%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25A8%259E%25E6%25A9%259F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=dc280a7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%A8%9E%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"c597d59823e1d7b7c5e3df9213716a68b6126b85","tid":2149990,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"李柱銘"},{"pid":"90d593c032eafe612bd3470337b89af2106cecab","tid":